sourcesContent:
<style lang="scss">
.popup{
  background-color: aqua;
}
ul{
  padding-left: 0;
  li {
    list-style: none;
  }
}
a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #444;
}
.about {
  background-image: url("../img/kureinn2201004.jpeg");
  height: 100vh;
  width: 95vw;
  border-radius: 5%;
  background-size: cover;
  margin: 0 auto;
  #hoge {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  background-size: cover;
  padding-top: 100px;
    .content {
      width: 150px;
      height: 300px;
      background-color: #98f305fc;
      border-radius: 5%;
      color: #111;
      box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px #96f40057;
        button {
          display: block;
        }
      }
  }
  #hoge-con {
    margin: 0 auto;
    .popup-content{
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
        background-color: rgb(0, 200, 0);
        border-radius: 30%;
        margin-top: 100px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px #;
        position: fixed;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
        z-index: 1;
        .btn-box{
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-around;
          a {
            background-color: white;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 30%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
            height: 60px;
            padding-top: 10%;
          }
        }
        .sikaku{
          display: block;
          border: 1px solid white;
          background-color: white;
          margin : 0 auto 10px auto;
          width: 80%;
          border-radius: 5%;
        }
        .record-text{
          width: 200px;
          height: 100px;
          font-size: 30%;
        }
        .record-btn{
          background-color: white;
          width: 100px;
          height: 40px;
          font-size: 50%;
          border-radius: 10%;
        }
    }
    #step2{
      h5{
        background-color: white;
        width: 10%;
        height: 10%;
        display: inline;
      }
    }
    #step3{
      li{
        background-color: white;
        width: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 15px auto;
        border-radius: 10%;
      }
    }
  }
  .hide{
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
    background-color: rgb(57, 56, 56);
    opacity: 0.5;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0px;
    left: 0px;
    z-index: 0;
  }
}
</style>
